      • addArtisanJavascriptInterfaceToWebView

        public static void addArtisanJavascriptInterfaceToWebView(android.app.Activity activity,
                                          android.webkit.WebView webView)
        Add an Artisan Javascript interface to your webview. This will allow you to call standard Android SDK methods from the Javascript API.
        Parameters:
        activity - The activity that contains the WebView parameter.
        webView - The WebView that you wish to hook up with the Artisan Javascript API.
